<title>SAIL HOME!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuipi lien leh lauhum ahin,
 Kumsawt gam zuonin na tawl hi;
 Na Captainpa tawh na hih chun,
 Tawlin! tawlin! tawl in!

[V2]
 Tawlin! tawlin! huihpi bei pai tana,
 Thimna chuh kitawl mang tana!
 Tawlin! tawlin! Pathien A hing!
 Ma A pui hi, tawl in!

[V3]
 2. Buoi lo hiel in A hun tawl hi,
 Tuikinawk, huihpi hung mahleh;
 Huih nungin, tuikinawk mahleh,
 Tawlin! tawlin! tawlin!

[V4]
 3. Tuilien in, huih hat mahlele,
 Zing chengin lui gal na naih zel;
 Nitak chengin na naih deuh deuh,
 Tawlin! tawlin! tawlin!

[V5]
 4. Lawngchawlhna mun chuh a nai ta'i,
 Tawlin, na puonlap chuh a phe'i;
 Tui chin hetna chun en zelin,
 Tawlin! tawlin! tawlin!

[V6]
 5. Tuilien in a hun subuoi em?
 Guohpi huihpi a lauhum em?
 Pangin! Pathien thu zuou ngeilo!
 Tawlin! tawlin! tawlin!</lyrics>
</song>